      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4801">
            <h1 id="director-general-chief-economic-adviser">Director General, Chief Economic Adviser </h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>Responsibilities include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>ensuring the delivery of HM Treasury’s work programme, in particular supporting the government’s objectives to promote macroeconomic stability and maintain confidence in the macro policy framework: to promote sustainable economic growth and to ensure stable and sustainable tax receipts to fund government spending in the least distortive way</li>
  <li>leading the Treasury’s relationships with the monetary policy side of Bank of England, IMF, OECD and EC on UK Surveillance, gilt investment community, BEIS on growth and the CBI and wider economics community</li>
  <li>leading the Government Economic Service, chairing the GES Chief Economists Board</li>
</ul>
</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/hm-treasury">HM Treasury</a>
</p>

